file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: "1.0.0"
  title: "Dummy endpoints for testing"
  description: "A sample API containing some dummy endpoints for testing"
  license:
    name: "MIT"
paths:
  /dummy-response:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: "A dummy GET response"
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                dummy:
                  value:
                    status: "GET ok"
    post:
      responses:
        201:
          description: "A dummy POST response"
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                dummy:
                  value:
                    status: "POST ok"
    put:
      responses:
        200:
          description: "A dummy PUT response"
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                dummy:
                  value:
                    status: "PUT ok"
    patch:
      responses:
        200:
          description: "A dummy PATCH response"
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                dummy:
                  value:
                    status: "PATCH ok"
    delete:
      responses:
        200:
          description: "A dummy DELETE response"
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                dummy:
                  value:
                    status: "DELETE ok"
  /secure-dummy-response:
      get:
        security:
          - basicAuth: []
          - apiKey: []
          - oAuth: [read:data]
        responses:
          200:
            description: "A dummy but auth-checked GET response"
            content:
              application/json:
                examples:
                  dummy:
                    value:
                      status: "GET ok"
      post:
        security:
          - basicAuth: []
          - apiKey: []
          - oAuth: [write:data]
        responses:
          201:
            description: "A dummy but auth-checked POST response"
            content:
              application/json:
                examples:
                  dummy:
                    value:
                      status: "POST ok"
      put:
        security:
          - basicAuth: []
          - apiKey: []
          - oAuth: [write:data]
        responses:
          200:
            description: "A dummy but auth-checked PUT response"
            content:
              application/json:
                examples:
                  dummy:
                    value:
                      status: "PUT ok"
      patch:
        security:
          - basicAuth: []
          - apiKey: []
          - oAuth: [write:data]
        responses:
          200:
            description: "A dummy but auth-checked PATCH response"
            content:
              application/json:
                examples:
                  dummy:
                    value:
                      status: "PATCH ok"
      delete:
        security:
          - basicAuth: []
          - apiKey: []
          - oAuth: [write:data]
        responses:
          200:
            description: "A dummy but auth-checked DELETE response"
            content:
              application/json:
                examples:
                  dummy:
                    value:
                      status: "DELETE ok"
components:
  securitySchemes:
    basicAuth:
      type: "http"
      scheme: "basic"
    apiKey:
      type: "apiKey"
      name: "api_key_in_header"
      in: "header"
    oAuth:
      type: "oauth2"
      flows:
        implicit:
          authorizationUrl: "https://example.com/api/oauth/dialog"
          scopes:
            write:data: "modify some data in your account"
            read:data: "read your data"
